1.Display messages retrieved from the parse server.

2.Setup a way to refresh the displayed messages (either automatically or with a button).

3.Be careful to use proper escaping on any user input. Since you're
displaying input that other users have typed, your app is vulnerable to
XSS attacks.

4.Note: If you issue an XSS attack, please make it innocuous enough to be educational, rather than disruptive.

5. Allow users to select a username and send messages